Class EncryptedInitiateMultipartUploadRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.AmazonWebServiceRequest

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MaterialsDescriptionProvider

    public class EncryptedInitiateMultipartUploadRequest
extends InitiateMultipartUploadRequest
implements MaterialsDescriptionProvider

    This class is an extension of InitiateMultipartUploadRequest to allow additional encryption material description to be specified on a per-request basis. In particular, EncryptedInitiateMultipartUploadRequest is only recognized by AmazonS3EncryptionJavaClient.

    If EncryptedInitiateMultipartUploadRequest is used against the non-encrypting AmazonS3JavaClient, these additional attributes will be ignored.
